MODULE 2BITADDER

IMPORT FULLADDER

INPUT A[2]
INPUT B[2]

WIRE A0
WIRE A1
WIRE B0
WIRE B1
WIRE C0
WIRE C1
WIRE D0
WIRE D1
WIRE E0
WIRE E1
WIRE F0
WIRE F1

OUTPUT SUM[2]
OUTPUT CARRY

SPLIT A A0 A1
SPLIT B B0 B1

FULLADDER FA1 A0 B0 C0 C1
FULLADDER FA2 A1 B1 D0 D1
FULLADDER FA3 D1 C0 E0 E1
FULLADDER FA4 E1 C1 F0 F1

JOIN E0 D0 SUM
BUF BU1 F0 CARRY 


